Todd, good to have you on the list.

First things first, you started off great, but went down hill after that, be
sure to refer to your new to you type 2 as a BUS.  And yes, if you don't
treat it or call it correctly, your bus will make you pay for it!!

Don't remove the heads, shoot a couple good squirts of transmission oil down
the spark plug holes and wait a couple days before you try to turn the
engine over if you are worried about seized rings.

 
